---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Pillar from '../components/Pillar.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import ActionButton from '../components/ActionButton.astro';
---

<Layout title="Vorgo Space">
  <main class="grid min-h-full py-6 lg:px-8 px-6">
    <div id="center" class="text-center">
      <section class="flex flex-col my-14">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-grid"></div>
          <div
            class="font-extrabold md:text-6xl text-5xl md:leading-[5rem] sm:leading-[4rem] leading-[3rem] tracking-tight font-gilmer-heavy"
          >
            A Safe and Inclusive Community for Your <span class="text-[#FF9431]">Personal and Professional Growth</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="sm:px-16 my-14 font-semibold md:text-2xl text-xl md:leading-[2.7rem] sm:leading-10 leading-7 tracking-normal font-gilmer-medium opacity-70"
          >
            At the core, we believe by coming together, we can create a supportive and encouraging environment that
            allows individuals to learn from one another, grow personally and professionally to achieve our goals.
          </div>
          <ActionButton />
        </div>
      </section>
      <div>
        <div class="mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
              <p class="md:text-5xl text-4xl font-gilmer-heavy">
                What's <span class="text-[#FF9431]">in it</span> for me?
              </p>
              <p class="mt-10 text-xl text-muted font-gilmer-medium">
                Here is the list of awesome reasons for you to join our community to unlock new adventures and
                opportunities
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative cards">
              <div class="bg-starry"></div>
              <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-20 lg:mt-18">
                <div
                  class="grid gap-x-8 gap-y-8 lg:max-w-none grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 auto-rows-fr text-left"
                >
                  <Card
                    title="Personal and professional growth"
                    description="You'll have access to various resources and opportunities that will help you develop your skills, knowledge, and experience. Whether through workshops, events, mentorship, or collaboration, you'll be able to grow personally and professionally."
                  />
                  <Card
                    title="Opportunities to learn and explore"
                    description="Our community is a space to try new things and explore new ideas. We encourage our members to take risks, think outside the box, and learn from one another. You'll have access to a wealth of knowledge and resources to help you expand your horizons and discover new passions."
                  />
                  <Card
                    title="A supportive and inclusive environment"
                    description="One of the most significant benefits is the sense of belonging and support you'll feel. We prioritize creating a safe and inclusive space where everyone feels welcome and valued. You'll be able to connect with like-minded individuals who share your interests and goals."
                  />
                  <Card
                    title="Develop your personal brand"
                    description="Joining the community and sharing your knowledge and expertise can help you develop a personal brand by establishing yourself as a thought leader, increasing your visibility, building trust and credibility, and leading to new opportunities."
                  />
                  <Card
                    title="Leadership and mentorship opportunities"
                    description="If you are a seasoned professional, you likely have much to offer regarding leadership and mentorship. You can mentor younger members, lead community projects, or even start your venture."
                  />
                  <Card
                    title="Networking opportunities"
                    description="By joining this community, you'll have the chance to connect with other professionals in your field, share your expertise, and learn from others. You may even meet potential collaborators or partners for future projects."
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-starry"></div>
            <div class="py-16 sm:py-32 mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center pb-10">
              <p class="md:text-5xl text-4xl font-gilmer-heavy">
                Community <span class="text-[#FF9431]">pillars</span>
              </p>
              <p class="mt-10 text-xl text-muted font-gilmer-medium">
                Focused on these four areas, we foster a culture that prizes innovation, entrepreneurial spirit,
                quality, and diversity.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-pillars"></div>
            <Pillar
              title="Engineering"
              description="Being part of the engineering community empowers individuals to use technology to solve real-world problems, collaborate with like-minded individuals, and stay up-to-date with new technologies and trends."
            />
            <Pillar
              title="Craftsmanship"
              description="Promoting craftsmanship culture emphasizes the importance of quality work, attention to detail, and continuous learning while fostering a sense of pride and fulfilment in one's work as individuals strive to create something of lasting value and beauty."
            />
            <Pillar
              title="Entrepreneurship"
              description="By fostering a culture of entrepreneurship, we empower individuals to pursue their own ventures, create innovative products that drive positive change, and overcome challenges to achieve their goals."
            />
            <Pillar
              title="Diversity"
              description="Diversity brings a range of perspectives and experiences, which can lead to more innovative and effective problem-solving. When people from different backgrounds and cultures work together, they can bring unique solutions to the table and challenge each other's assumptions, leading to better outcomes."
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="flex flex-col items-center my-36 mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-starry h-[55vh]"></div>
          <div
            class="font-extrabold md:text-5xl text-4xl md:leading-[3.7rem] leading-[3rem] tracking-tight font-gilmer-heavy text-center text-white"
          >
            Elevate <span class="text-[#FF9431]">your</span> journey
          </div>
          <div
            class="px-16 mt-9 mb-12 font-semibold md:text-2xl text-xl tracking-normal font-gilmer-medium text-center opacity-70 text-white"
          >
            Join our community of forward-thinking professionals.
          </div>
          <ActionButton />
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
